name: NXTLVL Media, LLC
overview:
NXTLVL Media, LLC is an online Retailer, Publisher, Media and Event Production Company based in Houston, Texas.

NXTLVL Media, LLC produces and maintains NXTLVLMAG.com, the online home of NXTLVL Magazine, a Post-Evangelical Christian voice for those looking for depth and significance in an increasingly lacking Church and Society.

NXTLVL Media, LLC also operates the LE-RAQ Collective, a membership-based, boutique-style Business Development/Incubation firm serving Start-Up urban fashion brands, as well as LE-RAQ.com, our soon-coming online “Flash Sale” website serving as the retail outlet for LE-RAQ Collective members and the best in Urban and Street Apparel and music.
